'''Kevin Duván Castaño Gil''' (born 29 September 2000) is a Colombian professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[defensive midfielder]] for [[Argentine Primera División]] club [[Club Atlético River Plate|River Plate]] and the [[Colombia national football team|Colombia national team]].

A product of [[Águilas Doradas]], Castaño established himself in Colombia before moving abroad in 2023 to join [[Cruz Azul]] in Mexico. He later transferred to [[FC Krasnodar]], where he won the [[2024–25 Russian Premier League|Russian Premier League]] in his first season, the club’s first league title in history. In 2025, he signed with [[Club Atlético River Plate|River Plate]] in Argentina.

At international level, Castaño made his senior debut for Colombia in 2023 and was part of the squad that finished runners-up at the [[2024 Copa América]].

==Club career==
===Águilas Doradas===
Born in [[Itagüí]], Castaño came through the academy system at [[Águilas Doradas]] having joined when he was 12 years old.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://aguilasdoradas.com.co/equipoprofesional-dorado-de-seleccion-kevin-castano-citado-al-microciclo-de-trabajos-con-colombia/|accessdate=22 March 2023|title=Professional Team Selection gilding. Kevin Castaño cited to the microcycle of work with Colombia|website=Aguilasdoradas.com|archive-date=22 March 2023|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20230322083731/https://aguilasdoradas.com.co/equipoprofesional-dorado-de-seleccion-kevin-castano-citado-al-microciclo-de-trabajos-con-colombia/|url-status=live}}</ref> By the age of fifteen he was promoted to their under-20 team, and at eighteen years-old made the step up to the senior team, and his debut professional debut followed two years later.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://caracol.com.co/2023/03/14/kevin-castano-sobre-su-convocatoria-puedo-aportar-mucho-a-la-seleccion-colombia/?outputType=amp|website=Carocol.com|title=Kevin Castaño on his call-up: I can contribute a lot to the Colombian National Team|date=14 March 2023|accessdate=22 March 2023|archive-date=22 March 2023|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20230322084930/https://caracol.com.co/2023/03/14/kevin-castano-sobre-su-convocatoria-puedo-aportar-mucho-a-la-seleccion-colombia/?outputType=amp|url-status=live}}</ref>

===Cruz Azul===
On 26 June 2023, Castaño joined [[Cruz Azul]].<ref>{{Cite web|title=Kevin Castaño llega a México para reforzar a Cruz Azul|url=https://www.excelsior.com.mx/adrenalina/kevin-castano-llega-a-mexico-para-reforzar-a-cruz-azul/1593641|date=22 June 2023|website=Excélsior|language=es|access-date=22 June 2023|archive-date=3 July 2023|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20230703052623/https://www.excelsior.com.mx/adrenalina/kevin-castano-llega-a-mexico-para-reforzar-a-cruz-azul/1593641|url-status=live}}</ref>

===Krasnodar===
On 5 January 2024, Castaño agreed on a transfer to the Russian club [[FC Krasnodar|Krasnodar]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=FC Krasnodar|url=https://fckrasnodar.ru/team/news/object/?object_id=146023|title=КЕВИН КАСТАНЬО ПЕРЕХОДИТ В "КРАСНОДАР"|date=5 January 2024|language=ru|access-date=5 January 2024|archive-date=5 January 2024|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20240105113902/https://fckrasnodar.ru/team/news/object/?object_id=146023|url-status=live}}</ref> Signing a contract until the summer of 2028 on 21 January 2024.<ref>{{cite web |title=КЕВИН КАСТАНЬО СТАЛ ИГРОКОМ "КРАСНОДАРА" |url=https://fckrasnodar.ru/team/news/object/?object_id=146056 |website=fckrasnodar.ru/ |publisher=FC Krasnodar |access-date=26 March 2024 |language=Russian |date=21 January 2024 |archive-date=26 March 2024 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20240326110234/https://fckrasnodar.ru/team/news/object/?object_id=146056 |url-status=live }}</ref>

===River Plate===
On 12 March 2025, Castaño signed with [[Club Atlético River Plate|River Plate]] in Argentina.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=River Plate|url=https://www.cariverplate.com.ar/kevin-casta-o-nuevo-jugador-de-river-plate|title=Kevin Castaño, nuevo jugador de River Plate|trans-title=Kevin Castaño, new River Plate player|date=13 March 2025|language=ru}}</ref>

==International career==
Castano made his debut for the [[Colombia national football team|Colombia]] senior side in a friendly match against the [[United States men's national soccer team|United States]] on 28 January 2023.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://espndeportes.espn.com/futbol/mundial/nota/_/id/11754625/alvaro-montero-kevin-castano-nelson-palacio-representan-fpc-seleccion-colombia?platform=amp|title=Álvaro Montero, Kevin Castaño, Juanfer Quintero and Nelson Palacio, the contribution of the FPC for the friendlies against Korea and Japan|website=ESPN.com|date=13 March 2023|accessdate=22 March 2023|archive-date=22 March 2023|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20230322082903/https://espndeportes.espn.com/futbol/mundial/nota/_/id/11754625/alvaro-montero-kevin-castano-nelson-palacio-representan-fpc-seleccion-colombia?platform=amp|url-status=live}}</ref> He was called up again to the Colombia squad for friendly matches against [[South Korea national football team|South Korea]] and [[Japan national football team|Japan]] in March 2023.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.espn.com.co/futbol/colombia/nota/_/id/11754990/kevin-castano-entrevista-espn-f90-me-siento-preparado-para-jugar-en-seleccion-colombia?platform=amp|website=espn.com|accessdate=22 March 2023|title=Kevin Castaño is confident of earning a place in Néstor Lorenzo's team|date=13 March 2023|archive-date=22 March 2023|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20230322082103/https://www.espn.com.co/futbol/colombia/nota/_/id/11754990/kevin-castano-entrevista-espn-f90-me-siento-preparado-para-jugar-en-seleccion-colombia?platform=amp|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://colombia.as.com/videos/kevin-castano-mi-primer-llamado-a-seleccion-es-una-motivacion-v/|website=colombia.as.com|accessdate=22 March 2023|date=14 March 2023|title=Kevin Castaño: "My first call-up to the National Team is motivation"|archive-date=22 March 2023|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20230322082406/https://colombia.as.com/videos/kevin-castano-mi-primer-llamado-a-seleccion-es-una-motivacion-v/|url-status=live}}</ref>

==Personal life==
His father Richard, with whom he would have training sessions as a youngster, was a big influence on his football career.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.noticiasrcn.com/deportes/este-es-kevin-castano-de-los-mejores-volantes-del-fpc-que-recibio-un-llamado-a-seleccion-441977|title=This is Kevin Castaño: one of the best midfielders of the FPC who received a call to the National Team|date=13 March 2023|accessdate=22 March 2023|archive-date=22 March 2023|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20230322084506/https://www.noticiasrcn.com/amp/deportes/quien-es-kevin-castano-convocado-seleccion-colombia-441977|url-status=live}}</ref>

